<facsimile><graphic url="https://www.e-manuscripta.ch/i3f/v20/1079379/manifest"/></facsimile><text><body><div type="letter">
<pb facs="1079380" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Illustrissimo ac Celeberrimo Viro
  <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Joanni Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>
  <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelottus</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
<p>Jamdiu est quod bonatissimi tui Filii <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Danielis</rs> in hanc
         <lb/>civitatem advent<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> frustra expecto. Quidnam caus<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>fuerit quod ipse clarissimus tuus <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filius</rs> in <rs key="place_KON-italie" type="place">Italiam</rs>
<lb/>nostram nondum advenerit, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te, Amicissime Vir,
         <lb/>scire aveo; quanquam eum fortasse hac de re ali<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quando ad me scripturum spero. Clarissimum
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Jac. Jurinum</rs> <rs type="organisation">Regi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Societati <rs type="place">Londinensi</rs></rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Secretis,
         <lb/>humanissimas ad me dedisse <rs type="letter">litteras</rs><note type="internal">Brief nachweisen in Nachlass Michelotti.</note>, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> modo me<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>morato summ<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> virtutis tuo <rs type="person">Filio</rs>, Te fieri certiorem
         <lb/>ante mens<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> circiter curavi, quidque ad me scripserit
         <lb/>id<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119507978" type="person">Jurinus</rs> indicavi. In pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentia vero Tibi, Sapien<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tissime Vir, significo me ipsimet <choice><abbr>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clariss.</abbr><expan>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clarissimo</expan></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119507978">Jurino</rs>
<lb/>jam respondisse, rescripturumque quid de suis
         <lb/>in tuam <abbr>ingeniosiss.<hi rend="sup">am</hi></abbr> de velocitat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per
         <lb/>foramen vasis effluentis demonstration<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ani<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>madversionibus,<note type="internal">Nachweisen, worum es bei den Animadversionibus geht. Evtl. Dissertationis de motu aquarum fluentium contra nonnullas Petri Antonii Michelotti animadversiones Defensio, Venedig 1724 </note> ego vicissim sentiam, vel po<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tius Te sentire putem, spopondisse. Statim ac
  <lb/>Animadversiones <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119507978">Jurinianas</rs> accepero Te faciam
         <lb/>certiorem.</p> <closer><salute>Tu interim fac ut valeas, meque ama<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re (quod vehementer opto) pergas.</salute>
<dateline><choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Dabam</expan></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice>
  <lb/><date when="1723-04-16">16 Aprilis 1723</date>.</dateline></closer>
<pb facs="1079381" n="2"/>
<figure facs="1079381_01.png" hand="pers_DE-588-102552517"><figDesc/></figure>
<postscript><p><abbr>P. S.</abbr> </p>
<p>Aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> de vase cylindrico <formula>ABE</formula><del>effluen</del> per foramen <formula>EF</formula> effluen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis tempore dato <formula>t</formula>, <add>quantitatem</add> non maiorem esse quantitate
            <lb/>ejusdem aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in cylindro <formula>AE</formula> content<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> probare
            <lb/>conatus fuit Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantissimus <add>t</add>uus Filius <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Daniel</rs>
<lb/><rs key="B_1723-01-16_991170430253405501" type="letter">litteris <date when="1723-01-16">16 Januarii</date> ad me perscriptis</rs>. Illis enim
            <lb/>ipsis <rs type="letter">litteris</rs> cylindr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> aque<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <formula>ST</formula> ead<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ratione
            <lb/>longitudine superare cylindr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <formula>AF</formula>, ac ab hoc
            <lb/>latitudine superatur, ideoque hos duos cylindros
            <lb/>aqueos <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quales esse inter se, demonstrare alla<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>boravit. Dixit<note type="internal"></note> ergo quod guttul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>F</formula>, <formula>Q</formula>, <formula>N</formula>, <formula>P</formula>, conflu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>unt (propterea quod aqua non est fluidissima) at<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que hac ratione eas cylindrulum tenuior<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>, seu gra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ciliorem <formula>ST</formula> constituere. Ego autem ut Cylin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>drum aque<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <formula>FM</formula> longior<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> esse cylindro <formula>AF</formula> eand<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
            <lb/>cum illo basim habente (posita aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> summa
            <lb/>fluiditate) libenter <add>do</add>, sic aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> guttulis
            <lb/><formula>F</formula>, <formula>Q</formula>, <formula>N</formula>, <formula>P</formula> confluentibus, sive magis ad se accedenti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus graciliorem evadere cylindrum <formula>FM</formula>, non
            <lb/>clare intelligo; mihi potius videtur ips<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
            <pb facs="1079382" n="3"/>
<lb/>cylindr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <formula>FM</formula> confluentibus aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> guttulis <formula>F</formula>, <formula>Q</formula>, <formula>N</formula>, <formula>P</formula><choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice>
            <lb/>brevior<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> fieri debere; ideo enim longior <add>esset</add>, quia
            <lb/>interstitiola remanerent posita summa
  <lb/>aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fluiditate. <choice><orig>propter</orig><reg>Propter</reg></choice> <choice><sic><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualitem</sic><corr><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualitatem</corr></choice> actionis, et
            <lb/>retroactionis guttular<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per foramen <formula>EF</formula>
<lb/>egredienti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>. Ego ut hujusmodi me<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> difficulta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem examines, quidne de ea Tibi videatur,
            <lb/>ad me scribere ne graveris etiam atque
            <lb/>etiam rogo, ac qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so; Vale iter<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, Illustrissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>me Vir, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118656503">Filiumque</rs> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> aliquando ad
  <lb/>me mitte.</p></postscript>
